<div class="policy-page page-width">
  {% render 'breadcrumbs' %}

  <div class="policy-hero animate-on-scroll fade-up">
    <span class="text-eyebrow">Legal &amp; Policies</span>
    <h1>Shipping &amp; Refund Policy</h1>
    <p>Effective Date: July 1, 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-body">

    <!-- ═══ SHIPPING POLICY ═══ -->
    <section class="policy-section animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <div class="policy-section__icon">🚚</div>
      <h2>Shipping Policy</h2>
      <p>Welcome to Tokiyo Lifestyle! We are committed to delivering your orders safely, quickly, and efficiently.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="policy-grid">

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Order Processing</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Orders are processed within <strong>1–3 business days</strong> after successful payment confirmation.</li>
          <li>Orders placed on Sundays or public holidays will be processed on the next business day.</li>
          <li>During product launches, festive seasons, or sale events, processing may take slightly longer.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">🚚</div>
        <h3>Shipping Coverage</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>We currently ship <strong>across India</strong> and are working towards expanding our services internationally.</li>
          <li>If your location is serviceable by our logistics partners, we'll deliver your order right to your doorstep.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">⏱️</div>
        <h3>Estimated Delivery Time</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Metro Cities:</strong> 2–5 business days</li>
          <li><strong>Tier 2 &amp; Tier 3 Cities:</strong> 3–7 business days</li>
          <li><strong>Remote Locations:</strong> 5–10 business days</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="policy-card__note">Delivery timelines are estimates and may vary due to weather, courier delays, public holidays, or other unforeseen circumstances.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">💳</div>
        <h3>Shipping Charges</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Shipping charges (if applicable) will be displayed during checkout before you complete your order.</li>
          <li>We may offer <strong>free shipping</strong> on eligible orders during promotions or above a minimum order value.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📍</div>
        <h3>Order Tracking</h3>
        <p>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a tracking link via <strong>email, SMS, or WhatsApp</strong> (where applicable), allowing you to monitor your shipment in real time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Delivery Attempts</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Our courier partner will make multiple delivery attempts.</li>
          <li>If delivery cannot be completed due to an incorrect address, unavailable recipient, or repeated failed attempts, the order may be returned to us.</li>
          <li>Additional shipping charges may apply for re-dispatch.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📝</div>
        <h3>Incorrect Shipping Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Please ensure your <strong>shipping address, mobile number, and PIN code</strong> are accurate before placing your order.</li>
          <li>Tokiyo Lifestyle is not responsible for delays or failed deliveries caused by incorrect information provided by the customer.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Damaged or Tampered Packages</h3>
        <p>If your package appears damaged or tampered with at the time of delivery:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Do not accept the package if possible.</li>
          <li>Take clear photos of the package.</li>
          <li>Contact our support team within <strong>24 hours of delivery</strong>.</li>
          <li>We'll investigate the issue and assist you as quickly as possible.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">🌍</div>
        <h3>International Shipping</h3>
        <p>International shipping is currently <strong>unavailable</strong>. We look forward to serving customers worldwide in the near future.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ═══ DIVIDER ═══ -->
    <div class="policy-divider animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <span>Return, Exchange &amp; Refund Policy</span>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ REFUND POLICY ═══ -->
    <section class="policy-section animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <div class="policy-section__icon">🔄</div>
      <h2>Return, Exchange &amp; Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>At Tokiyo Lifestyle, we are committed to delivering premium-quality products and a great shopping experience. If something isn't right, we're here to help.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="policy-grid">

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Return Eligibility</h3>
        <p>You may request a return or exchange if:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You received a <strong>damaged or defective</strong> product.</li>
          <li>You received the <strong>wrong item or incorrect size</strong>.</li>
          <li>The product is <strong>unused, unwashed, and in its original condition</strong>.</li>
          <li>All original tags, labels, packaging, and accessories are intact.</li>
          <li>The return request is submitted within <strong>7 days</strong> of receiving your order.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card policy-card--warning animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">❌</div>
        <h3>Items Not Eligible for Return</h3>
        <p>Returns or exchanges will not be accepted if:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>The product has been <strong>used, washed, or altered</strong>.</li>
          <li>Original tags or packaging are missing.</li>
          <li>The product is damaged due to misuse or improper handling.</li>
          <li>The return request is made after the eligible return period.</li>
          <li>The product was purchased during a clearance or final sale (unless it arrived damaged or incorrect).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">🔄</div>
        <h3>Exchange Policy</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>If you need a different size or have received an incorrect product, we'll be happy to arrange an exchange, subject to stock availability.</li>
          <li>If the requested size or product is unavailable, you may choose a refund or store credit, as applicable.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Refund Policy</h3>
        <p>Once your returned product is received and passes our quality inspection:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Refunds for prepaid orders will be processed to the <strong>original payment method</strong>.</li>
          <li>COD refunds will be processed via <strong>bank transfer</strong> or another approved method.</li>
          <li>Refunds are generally processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong> after approval.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">🚚</div>
        <h3>Return Shipping</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>If the return is due to a <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect product</strong>, Tokiyo Lifestyle will bear the return shipping cost.</li>
          <li>For other eligible returns, return shipping terms will be communicated by our support team.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">📷</div>
        <h3>Damaged or Incorrect Products</h3>
        <p>If you receive a damaged, defective, or incorrect item:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Take clear photos of the product and packaging.</li>
          <li>Contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong>.</li>
          <li>Share your order number and supporting images.</li>
          <li>Our team will review your request and resolve it as quickly as possible.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-card animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="policy-card__icon">🚫</div>
        <h3>Order Cancellation</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Orders can be cancelled <strong>before they are shipped</strong>.</li>
          <li>Once an order has been dispatched, it cannot be cancelled. However, eligible return or exchange requests can be made after delivery.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ═══ CONTACT CTA ═══ -->
    <div class="policy-cta animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <div class="policy-cta__inner">
        <h3>Need Help?</h3>
        <p>For any shipping, return, exchange, or refund queries, our team is here for you.</p>
        <a href="mailto:info@tokiyolifestyle.com" class="button button--solid">
          📧 info@tokiyolifestyle.com
        </a>
        <p class="policy-cta__tagline">Made in India. Designed for the World. ❤️</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    padding-block: 3rem 5rem;
  }
  .policy-hero {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }
  .policy-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .policy-hero p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #767674);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .policy-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #0A0A0A;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .policy-section__icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .policy-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .policy-section p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .policy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  @media(max-width: 989px) {
    .policy-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media(max-width: 600px) {
    .policy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, rgba(0,0,0,0.07));
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .policy-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .policy-card--warning {
    border-color: rgba(198, 40, 40, 0.2);
    background: #FFF8F8;
  }
  .policy-card__icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .policy-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-primary, #111111);
  }
  .policy-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #767674);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .policy-card ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }
  .policy-card ul li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #767674);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .policy-card__note {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem !important;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #767674);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .policy-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 3.5rem 0;
  }
  .policy-divider::before,
  .policy-divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border, rgba(0,0,0,0.08));
  }
  .policy-divider span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #767674);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .policy-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .policy-cta__inner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .policy-cta__inner h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .policy-cta__inner > p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .policy-cta__tagline {
    margin-top: 1.5rem !important;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping & Refund Policy",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-policy"
}
{% endschema %}
